00:13:30.269 --> 00:13:32.568
"A vossa parte é "Scoop, Scoop".

00:13:32.568 --> 00:13:35.286
Soa assim: "Scoop, Scoop!"

00:13:35.286 --> 00:13:36.240
Soa assim.

